    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW194832467 BCX8">In a commentary published in The Lancet on 28 June 2023 researchers from Queen Margaret University’s Institute for Global Health and Development discuss one of the great dilemmas facing our world – how can we equitably share the inevitable harms from global heating across the world and what capacity do we have across our global systems to protect the most vulnerable?</span> </p>]]></Value>
